thread.section_title: Print24 Bewertungen | Kundenbewertungen von Print24 | print24.com
thread.title: Isabel

author: Isabel
title: Isabel
text: They have a huge amount of products and excellent customer service. Even though my print arrived slightly damaged the first time, they replaced it immediately and the second one was perfect. The only minus I would give is that bulk orders seem to be possible only from a very high amount of products orders. I ordered 10 postcards motives, of each 50. I had to pay the shipping 10x because it wasn't possible to have them delivered all together.
